{"tid":2339122,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"考古學家於捷克修道院尋獲據稱是「釘死耶穌」的釘子","createTime":"2020-12-24T11:52:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-24T14:28:16.000Z","uid":31314,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"033c51273e80ac33d97ff6a582e331767e309d36","tid":2339122,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T11:52:46.000Z","msg":"近日有考古學家稱在捷克的修道院中，發現了一個釘子，而他們認為這個釘子就是當初把耶穌釘死在十字架上的。不過在此之前，考古學家也曾發現過數十個與耶穌十字架有關的釘子，因此對於這次的新發現，專家抱持著懷疑態度。<br />\n<br />\n根據英國《太陽報》報導，考古學家稱在捷克米萊夫斯科的修道院工作時有個驚人的發現，他們在密室中找到了一個盒子，上面刻著「IR」，意思是「耶穌是國王」，盒子裡面裝著一個15公分長的釘子，他們認為就是當初把耶穌釘死在十字架上的釘子。專家還指出，這個密室過去放著15世紀初期波希米亞戰爭中留下的稀有文物。<br />\n<br />\n據布拉格廣播電台報導指出，雖然研究人員無法確定這個釘子是否來自真的十字架，不過可以確定這個聖物箱比聖毛魯斯的聖物箱還要大，據悉，聖毛魯斯的聖物箱放有聖毛魯斯、聖約翰及聖提摩太的屍體碎片。<br />\n發現這個釘子的其中一位專家吉日&middot;辛德拉洛（Jiř&iacute;&Scaron;indel&aacute;ř）表示，由於密室部分被胡賽人（Hussites）摧毀，因此沒有證據能證明釘子就是耶穌十字架上的，專家也將於明年驗證，而釘子上是否有古老的骨頭及木頭痕跡，將是研究的一個重點。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3030769749447c3fdf4989f62aa2abb308daadec","tid":2339122,"uid":335303,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T11:53:52.000Z","msg":"咁咪可以攞到耶穌DNA????<br />\n<br />\n好想同佢生個bb<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail2_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3735e8c186055429ec01602c7b1bf5e867d8d7c0","tid":2339122,"uid":23445,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T11:55:55.000Z","msg":"睇下有冇mic 字樣"},{"pid":"a8dbd893b52927e85b06bfb685347f5eac1fde5b","tid":2339122,"uid":31314,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3030769749447c3fdf4989f62aa2abb308daadec","tid":2339122,"uid":335303,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T11:53:52.000Z","msg":"咁咪可以攞到耶穌DNA????<br />\n<br />\n好想同佢生個bb<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail2_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T11:58:27.000Z","msg":"gay<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a234d6d79f8bd9e9b842c18ef5f0ba655627b7df","tid":2339122,"uid":20170,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T12:00:00.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">不過在此之前，考古學家也曾發現過數十個與耶穌十字架有關的釘子</span><br />\n耶穌成身都係窿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33660dcc4b54ab8e69e3cbfff33efb67f22343d8","tid":2339122,"uid":324629,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a234d6d79f8bd9e9b842c18ef5f0ba655627b7df","tid":2339122,"uid":20170,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T12:00:00.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">不過在此之前，考古學家也曾發現過數十個與耶穌十字架有關的釘子</span><br />\n耶穌成身都係窿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T12:52:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57d4f72cc00c77a5310909665f07ea9b27fd5c43","tid":2339122,"uid":261937,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T12:58:27.000Z","msg":"耶穌死於朗基努斯槍喎"},{"pid":"91368ce6dcc3aa936b33211bce0a9a8733acb3f6","tid":2339122,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T12:59:52.000Z","msg":"聖釘 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15ac84aa65ef5aa1b54b568dbf157482bae949e0","tid":2339122,"uid":91017,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"57d4f72cc00c77a5310909665f07ea9b27fd5c43","tid":2339122,"uid":261937,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T12:58:27.000Z","msg":"耶穌死於朗基努斯槍喎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T13:01:13.000Z","msg":"唔係, 係對落去試下佢瓜未"},{"pid":"e47644b53013048637316fb82975666b5a2498c7","tid":2339122,"uid":85629,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T13:07:08.